==English==
===Etymology===
From the Arabic {{ARchar|فم الحوت}} (''fam al-ḥūt'') ‘the whale's mouth’, from {{ARchar|[[فم]]}} ‘mouth’ + {{ARchar|[[حوت]]}} ‘whale’.

===Noun===
'''Formalhaut'''
# [[Alpha Piscis Austrini]], the brightest [[star]] in the [[constellation]] [[Piscis Austrinus]]

